correspondentProfile.headline: Propietario en Miski Reposteria
correspondentProfile.about:
Durante muchos años he trabajado en distintas emisoras de corte juvenil, así como en una ONG internacional, como lo es Radio Nederland, desempeñándome como locutora, productora y guionista. En las emisoras juveniles también fui animadora de eventos, incluso de tipo masivo. Esto me llevó más adelante, a participar como maestra de ceremonias en eventos más formales.

También he trabajado en televisión. Inicialmente, trabajé en Canal UCR siendo estudiante. Mi práctica profesional la hice en REPRETEL, como asistente de producción, y volví en el 2014 a Canal UCR, esta vez como productora audiovisual. Tuve la oportunidad de producir, dirigir y guionizar distintos tipos de producciones, desde un programa de cocina hasta dos documentales y una serie de spots. Posteriormente, trabajé en el Departamento de Producción Audiovisual de la UNED, también por contrato. Tuve a a cargo dos distintas producciones, y posteriormente trabajé como asistente.

De 2020 a 2022, trabajo dando clases de locución en línea a través de la Escuela deleFOCO. Creé tres niveles de este curso.

Me siento cómoda con un equipo de trabajo a cargo. Soy ágil resolviendo problemas y con las relaciones públicas. Soy creativa, me gusta innovar. Me gusta escribir, pero también sé transmitir mis ideas en imágenes y sonidos. Sin duda nací para comunicar.

I’m a results-driven business development leader passionate about creating lasting opportunities for individuals with disabilities. As Director of Business Development at Southwind Fields, I build strategic partnerships and secure funding to support programs that empower individuals to achieve greater independence and integration within their communities.

I oversee initiatives focused on employment, training, and career advancement, working to implement sustainable solutions that have a long-term impact. With extensive experience in grant writing and fundraising, I leverage a wide network of professional and community connections to help expand Southwind’s reach and resources.

Through my work, I strive to not only improve the lives of the individuals we serve but also strengthen the communities we partner with.

If you're interested in connecting or collaborating, feel free to reach out!

messages.body: TM, you’ve heard about us, right? We can give Southwind Fields a zero-prospecting week by routing live roles at firms that are buying staffing services (verified) + the HM contacts. If useful, I’ll send 3 sample leads today, or we can do a 15 min quick chat?

TM, quick confirm: 

- A) I DM 3 roles for Southwind Fields, or 

- B) 15 min call and I show you all leads? 

Reply A or B and I’ll follow your lead.

TM, quick proof for Southwind Fields: here’s the 30-sec video + case study (video + transcript): https://youtu.be/6Y4zdjkeoMo

If you’d rather see examples, let me know and we'll book a demo so I can show you leads in real time.

Not relevant? Let me know and I will stop reaching out to you.

Hi TM,

I tried to reach you a couple of times, but haven't heard back from you... 

Agency Leads delivers fresh leads daily and helps recruiters turn them into booked meetings.

In case you haven’t seen it, here’s a 30-second video that explains exactly how it works: https://youtu.be/6Y4zdjkeoMo

If that looks useful, grab a spot on my calendar here: https://calendly.com/agency-leads/agency-leads-premium-staffing-leads-c0095?utm_source=c0095&utm_content=zcrm_5721581000089412850&utm_medium=linkedin&utm_campaign=Emile_Ledaine

Hi, Emile. Thanks for the offer but I am not a recruiter for an organization. I am a Job Placement Specialist working with a group of job seekers who have slight intellectual disabilities. If you know of any employers who are  interested in creating a more inclusive and diverse workplace, please feel free to refer them to me. Many thanks.

Thanks for clarifying TM - your work with job seekers with disabilities sounds meaningful. Our product is for staffing agencies, so I had the wrong audience. I'll keep Southwind in mind if I hear of inclusive hiring initiatives. All the best!
Many thanks!

Check out those candidates and reach out to them via CazVid.
Can't we discuss here?

Of course Zeeshan! Happy to chat here.

CazVid is a free platform where you can post unlimited jobs and we automatically send them to matching candidates. Think of it as a video-based job board where candidates apply with short video resumes.

Here's a quick video that explains how it works: https://youtu.be/XJZcKKnymcU

You can post your jobs for free here: https://share.cazvid.app/cazvid3.0/en/free-job-posting?utm_source=linkedin&utm_medium=message&utm_campaign=Martinez&utm_content=candidate

Let me know if you have any other questions!
I have few questions,
Sure Zeeshan, go ahead! Happy to answer.

Thanks, Camila! The video-resume concept is actually really interesting definitely a fresh way to screen candidates.
I’m curious about the employer side how are you guys currently tracking the quality of the candidates being matched? Also, are you using any specific data tools to help your users identify the highest-intent applicants quickly?

Great questions Zeeshan!

For quality matching - when an employer posts a job, we automatically send it to the top 100 candidates who match the requirements. Those candidates then apply, and their applications (with video intros) go directly to the employer's email.

The "highest-intent" filter is really the video itself - you can quickly see communication skills, professionalism, and fit in 30-60 seconds, which saves hours of screening calls.

We don't have sophisticated data analytics tools built in yet - it's a pretty straightforward post > match > apply > hire flow. But that simplicity is also what keeps it free and easy to use.

Does that help clarify? Happy to dive deeper into any specific area.

That definitely clarifies things, thanks! The 'video as a filter' is a great way to gauge personality instantly.
It’s interesting you mentioned the data side,I actually built a dashboard called ZakVibe Intelligence specifically for that. We focus on identifying high-intent pipelines and tracking how outreach actually performs (we're seeing a 12.5% reply rate right now).
Since you’re currently in a 'straightforward' flow, would you be open to a quick look at how we track those engagement metrics? Might be some cool overlap for your employers down the road

Appreciate the offer Zeeshan! ZakVibe sounds interesting, but we're pretty focused on our current flow right now and not looking to add new tools at the moment.

If you ever need to hire for your team though, you know where to find us. Best of luck with the dashboard!
Thanks, Camila

messages.body:
Hey Edwin, you’ve heard about us right?

At Agency Leads, we’ve helped thousands of recruiters over the past 7 years secure new clients through verified job openings and direct access to hiring managers.

Here’s a 30-second video that shows exactly how: https://youtu.be/6Y4zdjkeoMo

Let’s discuss how we can help you too, Edwin. You can book a meeting with me here: https://calendly.com/agency-leads/agency-leads-premium-staffing-leads-c0101?utm_source=c0101&utm_content=zcrm_5721581000087952488&utm_medium=linkedin&utm_campaign=Anthony_Squillante

Edwin, would you find it helpful to have access to millions of verified job openings from companies that partner with recruitment agencies & executive search firms? 

At Agency Leads, that’s exactly what we’ve been providing for over 7 years. Founded by recruiters for recruiters, we specialize exclusively in the Staffing and Recruiting industry. 

See what our clients have to say about us here: https://www.trustpilot.com/review/agency-leads.com. The reviews speak for themselves! 

Let’s connect to discuss how we can help you get new clients for your recruitment business: 
https://calendly.com/agency-leads/agency-leads-premium-staffing-leads-c0101?utm_source=c0101&utm_content=zcrm_5721581000087952488&utm_medium=linkedin&utm_campaign=Anthony_Squillante

Hey Mohd, you’ve heard about us right?

At Agency Leads, we’ve helped thousands of recruiters over the past 7 years secure new clients through verified job openings and direct access to hiring managers.

Here’s a 30-second video that shows exactly how: https://youtu.be/6Y4zdjkeoMo

Let’s discuss how we can help you too, Mohd. You can book a meeting with me here: https://calendly.com/agency-leads/agency-leads-premium-staffing-leads-c0095?utm_source=c0095&utm_content=zcrm_5721581000089378320&utm_medium=linkedin&utm_campaign=Filip_Vandamme

Mohd, would you find it helpful to have access to millions of verified job openings from companies that partner with recruitment agencies & executive search firms? 

At Agency Leads, that’s exactly what we’ve been providing for over 7 years. Founded by recruiters for recruiters, we specialize exclusively in the Staffing and Recruiting industry. 

See what our clients have to say about us here: https://www.trustpilot.com/review/agency-leads.com. The reviews speak for themselves! 

Let’s connect to discuss how we can help you get new clients for your recruitment business: 
https://calendly.com/agency-leads/agency-leads-premium-staffing-leads-c0095?utm_source=c0095&utm_content=zcrm_5721581000089378320&utm_medium=linkedin&utm_campaign=Filip_Vandamme

Hi,

At Agency Leads, we specialize in providing top-quality leads for recruitment agencies and executive search firms. We offer access to millions of verified job openings and their hiring managers, ensuring they work with staffing agencies to fill their roles.

With Agency Leads, you can strategically focus your business development on companies that have been confirmed to collaborate with your competitors - we can even identify who those competitors are!

Check out our case studies here: https://agency-leads.com/case-studies/ 

Let's connect to help you secure new clients as soon as possible: https://calendly.com/agency-leads/agency-leads-premium-staffing-leads-c0095?utm_source=c0095&utm_medium=linkedin&utm_campaign=Filip_Vandamme

I tried to reach you a couple of times, but haven't heard back from you... 

Agency Leads delivers fresh leads daily and helps recruiters turn them into booked meetings.

In case you haven’t seen it, here’s a 30-second video that explains exactly how it works: https://youtu.be/6Y4zdjkeoMo

If that looks useful, grab a spot on my calendar here: https://calendly.com/agency-leads/agency-leads-premium-staffing-leads-c0095?utm_source=c0095&utm_content=zcrm_5721581000089378320&utm_medium=linkedin&utm_campaign=Filip_Vandamme

correspondentProfile.about:
Xploy is a full service outsourcing company that enables your business to stay competitive in a tight market, by hiring remote dedicated staff to do your office work in our offshore offices.

We do customer service, technical support, bookkeeping, billing, data entry, sales, and just about any office work.

The benefits of using our outsourcing services are plenty, here are some examples.

Bilingual, Our agents are fluent in Spanish and English.

Time Zone, Xploy employees are in the same time zone as you.

Security, We have full time managers and camera systems installed to keep tabs at all times, and you have full access to your employees call records, time sheets, and even screenshots of their computers.

We bill you as a service, and you write that off as a business expense, cutting payroll costs, taxes, workers comp, and more.

American Education, We proudly offer agents with an American education, agents that have studied, worked, and lived in the United States.

Cad, when it comes to Cad we have decades of experience in drafting in the greater New York area.

Reach out to me for a free consultation, and lets improve your bottom line.
